#

Savory Bacon Macaroni Bake

45 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Comfort FoodHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseComfort Food

Tags:

EasyBakedCheesy

Description

A creamy and cheesy macaroni dish baked to perfection with crispy bacon for that extra savory touch!

Ingredients

  • macaroni pasta: 2 cups
  • bacon: 6 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 2 cups
  • cream cheese: 1/2 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1/2 teaspoon
